toilet (0.1-2) unstable; urgency=high

  * debian/control:
    + Changed conflict to figlet (<= 2.2.1-4) so that toilet and figlet can
      be installed together in Etch.
    + Added Vcs fields.
  * debian/rules:
    + Fix a crash in filter.c triggered eg. by "echo | toilet -F rotate".

